                                    $25 USD for transfers from $501 USD to $1,000 USD.<br>
                                    You can include two or more registrations in a single transfer.</li> 
                        </ul>            
                        </div>
                </div>
                <form class="btnContainerInsc" action="/save" method="POST">
                    <input type="hidden" name="Firstname" value="<%= query.Firstname %>">
                    <input type="hidden" name="Lastname" value="<%= query.Lastname %>">
                    <input type="hidden" name="Email" value="<%= query.Email %>">
                    <input type="hidden" name="Federation" value="<%= query.Federation %>">
                    <input type="hidden" name="Country" value="<%= query.Country %>">
                    <input type="hidden" name="Ageclass" value="<%= query.Ageclass %>">
                    <input type="hidden" name="Gender" value="<%= query.Gender %>">
                    <input type="hidden" name="Bowtype" value="<%= query.Bowtype %>">
                    <input type="hidden" name="Target" value="<%= query.Target %>">
                    <input type="hidden" name="Flint" value="<%= query.Flint %>">
                    <input type="hidden" name="Mssg" value="<%= query.Mssg %>">
                    <button type="submit" class="btnInsc btnReg">Confirm</button>
                    <a class="btnInsc btnCnl" href="/">Cancel</a> 
                </form>
                <div class="insNotes">
                        <h2>NOTE</h2>
                        <li>Each inscription is only for one participant.
                        </li>
                        <li>After filling the form, you will get 14 days from the reservation to pay the registration fee and send the receipt to wiac2025@gmail.com
                        </li>
                        <li>After 14 days of the inscription, if you have not made the payment, your reservation will be <strong>CANCELED</strong> </li>
                        <li>After paying, you will get registered and you will get a spot in the WIAC 2025.</li>
                        <li>Note: Amounts will be charged in local currency (ARS).</li>
                        <li>Please read the <a class="aForm" href="/tyc">Terms of acceptance </a>before registration.</li>
                </div>

        </div>
        <div class="needHelpContainer">
